577
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:01,300
Quoi?

578
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:03,700
Comment tu...?

579
00:42:04,100 --> 00:42:05,900
Oh, Mon Dieu!

580
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:39,300
